{"word":"ἀνακλίνω","slug":"ἀνακλίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n6736\" key=\"a)nakli/nw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀνα-κλίνω</orth>, poet. <orth extent=\"pref\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀγκλ-</orth>, (v. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κλίνω</foreign>) <sense id=\"n6736.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lean</tr_> one thing <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">upon</tr_> another, [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τόξον] ποτὶ γαίῃ ἀγκλίνας</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">having laid</tr_> it on the ground, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:113\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.113</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ἔρως ἀνακλίνας τοῦ τόξου τὸν πῆχυν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1600.tlg001:2:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philostr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Im.\">Im.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.1</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. ἑαυτοὺς ἐπὶ τὸ ἐναντίον,</foreign> of sailors struggling against the wind, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg023:851b:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mech.\">Mech.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">851b13</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cause to recline</tr_> at table, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:31:4:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\