\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, of ground, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lie sloping upwards,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4080.tlg001:2:3:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gp.\">Gp.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.3.1</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n6736.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">push</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">put back,</tr_> and so, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">open,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">θύρην ἀγκλίνας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:156\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.156</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; so of the door of Olympus, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠμὲν ἀνακλῖναι πυκινὸν νέφος ἠδ᾽ ἐπιθεῖναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:751\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.751</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0533.tlg002:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Call.\">Call.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ap.\">Ap.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὴν θύρην τὴν καταπηκτὴν ἀ.,</foreign> i. e. the trap-door, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.16</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=